name: Don't Wake Up The Kitty !
description:
The kitty is sleeping and don't wake up her.

Tap or touch same color items and pop blocks to crush them quickly and rush before your screen fills!

When screen fills, alarm starts and the kitty will wake up. Be careful!

Challenge yourself and your friend with addictive cool action puzzle game.

Suitable for children and all ages. Enjoy it on iPhone, iPad and iPod touch.

Have fun !

■Game center support:
Compare your best top score with others in the world.

■Social sharing:
Share your new score and challenge with your friends circle.
